"黒砂の希少種":
"There has been a new sighting. A rare
variant of the large Darker Gwanahda,
called Gwanahda Nero, has popped up in
Lillipa's Desert. While there have been
sightings, many questions have been left
unanswered. Therefore, it would be best
to investigate this quickly. I'm counting
on you.

※Objetivos are Nv.41+ Gwanahda Neros."
